author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, the media have found their new racial martyr and victim of white supremacy. He’s a football player who got drafted into the NFL a few rounds later than expected. They don't make racial martyrs like they used to. Also, Trump has a judge arrested for interfering with immigration enforcement. An allegedly Republican governor vetoes a bill to keep sexually explicit material out of schools. And two gay influencers went out and purchased children through surrogacy. Now they spend their time parading the kids around and using them for content.
